From: Pietro Ameruoso <p.ameruoso@live.it>
Date: Wed, 2 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] boot: uboot-mediatek: Fix BPI-R4-Pro blue LED label typo

Fix typo in blue LED label from "blue:staus" to "blue:status" in the BPI-R4-Pro
8x device tree configuration.

Signed-off-by: Pietro Ameruoso <p.ameruoso@live.it>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a-bananapi-bpi-r4-pro-8x.dts | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/arch/arm/dts/mt7988a-bananapi-bpi-r4-pro-8x.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/dts/mt7988a-bananapi-bpi-r4-pro-8x.dtsi
@@ -769,7 +769,7 @@
 		};
 
 		led_blue: sys-led-blue {
-			label = "blue:staus";
+			label = "blue:status";
 			gpios = <&pca9555 14 GPIO_ACTIVE_HIGH>;
 		};
 	};
